# 📌 Project Overview

This project demonstrates a research workflow that combines AI-assisted literature synthesis with human verification.

The objective is not to trust AI-generated summaries automatically, but to evaluate, correct, and document weaknesses before integrating findings into policy recommendations.

Research Theme:

**How agricultural logistics and transport infrastructure influence rural economic productivity in Mindanao.**

